        "message": "Generate a security bulletin covering the top 8 most important cybersecurity stories from the last 72 hours. Sources: BleepingComputer, The Hacker News, Dark Web Informer, Kevin Beaumont.\n\nOutput ONLY the bulletin in this exact format:\n**Title:** ...\n**Summary:** (2-3 sentences)\n**Link:** ...\n\nSkip all narration. Do not explain what you are doing. Just output the compiled bulletin.",
        "model": "opencode-zen/glm-5-free",
        "timeoutSeconds": 600,
        "thinking": "off"
      },
      "delivery": {
        "mode": "announce",
        "channel": "telegram",
        "to": "YOUR_CHAT_ID",
        "bestEffort": true
      }
    },
